T*
(Vocabulary is a valuable part of English. Students perform better when they understand) Tj
T*
(word meaning, usage, and context clues, learn from examples such as using context to) Tj
T*
(infer the meaning of an unfamiliar word, and deliberately avoid mistakes like memorizing) Tj
